                            <li>Some Desperate Glory: Explores indoctrination, radicalization, and the power of found family in a high emotional stakes space opera.</li>
                            <li>The Murderbot Diaries (Novellas 1-4): Witty, action-packed sci-fi offering a humorous and engaging break with themes of identity and autonomy.</li>
                            <li>Binti Trilogy: Afrofuturist exploration of identity, culture, communication, and diplomacy on an interstellar stage.</li>
                            <li>The Vanished Birds: Lyrical, character-driven space opera focusing on love, loss, memory, and art.</li>
