                        <div class="event-details">
                            <p><strong>Weekly Load:</strong> ~7h/week.</p>
                            <p><strong>Theme & Concept:</strong> Acclaimed short story collection spanning fantasy, sci-fi, horror. Explores Black and marginalized experiences with Jemisin's signature insight.</p>
                            <p><strong>Why this Season:</strong> A fantastic collection to sample various speculative scenarios as the year winds down.</p>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article class="event-block">
                        <span class="event-block-date">November 29 - December 31, 2027 (Approx. 5 weeks): Buffer & Anticipation</span>
                        <div class="event-details">
                             <p><strong>Theme & Concept:</strong> Buffer Time / Catch-Up / Holiday Listening / Re-listens / Anticipated New Releases for late 2027/early 2028.</p>
                             <p><strong>Why this Season:</strong> This period allows flexibility. You might revisit favorites, catch up if any series ran longer, or pick up newly released books by favorite authors that fit your themes. Possible focus: Check for sequels to series started earlier (e.g., The Sixth World #3, Dark Star Trilogy #3, The Chronicles of Ghadid sequels if you opted for the series binge).</p>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article class="event-block">
