                         <div class="event-details">
                            <p><strong>Theme & Concept:</strong> Continue with any outstanding series sequels that may have released. Explore new standalone titles that have garnered attention in your preferred genres (Afrofuturism, Solarpunk, diverse Horror, Sociopolitical SF). Revisit an anthology for shorter listening experiences.</p>
                            <p><strong>Example (if Sixth World #3 is out):</strong> Black Sun Rising (The Sixth World #3) by Rebecca Roanhorse (approx 10-12h). (1 week)</p>
                            <p><strong>Example (if Dark Star #3 is out):</strong> White Wing, Dark Star (Dark Star Trilogy #3) by Marlon James (approx 24-26h). (1.5-2 weeks)</p>
