                    </div>
                    <p>This extended plan now robustly fills your listening schedule through Winter 2027/2028. The "series binge" rule means some periods are very dedicated to a single author or world. The later stages, especially into late 2027 and early 2028, have some built-in flexibility to accommodate the actual release dates of anticipated sequels or new discoveries. Always feel free to adjust based on your current listening mood and energy levels!</p>
